name: .ARPACK File Extension
summary: Learn about .ARPACK files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Plug-in file used by ArtRage digital painting software; stores an archive of data that adds new features to the software, such as new brush styles; allows the software to be customized.

content: ARPACK files can be installed by double-clicking them, assuming that ArtRage is installed.
